{
  "font_size": 0.4,
  "font_color": "#FFFFFF",
  "background_alpha": 0.5,
  "background_color": "#9C27B0",
  "Stroke": "none",
  "type": "AIsubtitle",
  "lang": "zh",
  "version": "eng-1.2.0-Index-johns-pen-lite",
  "body": [
    {
      "content": "我们通过组合构建模块来创建工作流程",
      "from": 0.12,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 1,
      "to": 4.12
    },
    {
      "content": "在本视频中我们将这些复杂工作流程进行序列化处理",
      "from": 4.12,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 2,
      "to": 8.48
    },
    {
      "content": "我想与大家分享几个关键设计模式",
      "from": 8.48,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 3,
      "to": 11.36
    },
    {
      "content": "这些是关于如何将构建模块组合成更复杂工作流程的思考模式",
      "from": 11.36,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 4,
      "to": 18.0
    },
    {
      "content": "让我们先看看",
      "from": 18.0,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 5,
      "to": 18.9
    },
    {
      "content": "我认为构建通用工作流程的四大关键设计模式是反射",
      "from": 18.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 6,
      "to": 23.14
    },
    {
      "content": "使用规划和多协作",
      "from": 23.14,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 7,
      "to": 26.29
    },
    {
      "content": "让我简要解释它们的含义",
      "from": 26.29,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 8,
      "to": 28.59
    },
    {
      "content": "然后我们将深入探讨这些模式的详细内容",
      "from": 28.59,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 9,
      "to": 33.389
    },
    {
      "content": "主要设计模式之一是反射",
      "from": 33.389,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 10,
      "to": 37.43
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我可能会向语言模型代理请求编写代码",
      "from": 37.43,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 11,
      "to": 40.97
    },
    {
      "content": "结果语言模型可能生成如下代码",
      "from": 40.97,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 12,
      "to": 44.93
    },
    {
      "content": "这里定义了一个用于特定任务的Python函数",
      "from": 44.93,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 13,
      "to": 47.95
    },
    {
      "content": "我随后可以构建如下提示",
      "from": 47.95,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 14,
      "to": 50.45
    },
    {
      "content": "这里提供了一段用于特定任务的代码",
      "from": 50.45,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 15,
      "to": 53.25
    },
    {
      "content": "然后复制粘贴",
      "from": 53.25,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 16,
      "to": 54.41
    },
    {
      "content": "将语言模型刚刚输出的内容放入此处",
      "from": 54.41,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 17,
      "to": 56.96
    },
    {
      "content": "然后我要求它",
      "from": 56.96,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 18,
      "to": 57.98
    },
    {
      "content": "仔细检查代码是否正确",
      "from": 57.98,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 19,
      "to": 59.5
    },
    {
      "content": "注重效率并给出建设性批评",
      "from": 59.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 20,
      "to": 61.72
    },
    {
      "content": "结果采用这种方式提示的语言模型",
      "from": 61.72,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 21,
      "to": 64.789
    },
    {
      "content": "可能能指出代码中的问题",
      "from": 64.789,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 22,
      "to": 67.709
    },
    {
      "content": "如果我将这些反馈重新输入模型",
      "from": 67.709,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 23,
      "to": 72.6
    },
    {
      "content": "说看起来存在一个错误",
      "from": 72.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 24,
      "to": 74.45
    },
    {
      "content": "能否修改代码修复它",
      "from": 74.45,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 25,
      "to": 76.15
    },
    {
      "content": "它可能会提供改进后的代码预览",
      "from": 76.15,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 26,
      "to": 82.85
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你能运行代码并查看执行结果",
      "from": 82.85,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 27,
      "to": 86.67
    },
    {
      "content": "将反馈输入语言模型",
      "from": 86.67,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 28,
      "to": 89.6
    },
    {
      "content": "也能使其迭代生成更优版本",
      "from": 89.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 29,
      "to": 93.84
    },
    {
      "content": "例如生成v3版本的代码",
      "from": 93.84,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 30,
      "to": 96.259
    },
    {
      "content": "因此反射是一种常见设计模式",
      "from": 96.259,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 31,
      "to": 98.519
    },
    {
      "content": "可让语言模型审查自身输出",
      "from": 98.519,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 32,
      "to": 101.499
    },
    {
      "content": "或引入外部信息源",
      "from": 101.499,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 33,
      "to": 105.039
    },
    {
      "content": "例如运行代码查看是否报错",
      "from": 105.039,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 34,
      "to": 108.47
    },
    {
      "content": "并将其作为反馈进行迭代",
      "from": 108.47,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 35,
      "to": 111.35
    },
    {
      "content": "从而生成更优的输出版本",
      "from": 111.35,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 36,
      "to": 113.95
    },
    {
      "content": "这种设计模式并非万能",
      "from": 113.95,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 37,
      "to": 116.09
    },
    {
      "content": "并不能保证百分之百成功",
      "from": 116.09,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 38,
      "to": 119.699
    },
    {
      "content": "但有时能显著提升系统性能",
      "from": 119.699,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 39,
      "to": 123.419
    },
    {
      "content": "现在我画出这个示意图",
      "from": 123.419,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 40,
      "to": 124.519
    },
    {
      "content": "显示为单一语言模型被调用",
      "from": 124.519,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 41,
      "to": 127.41
    },
    {
      "content": "但为预示多代理工作流程",
      "from": 127.41,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 42,
      "to": 130.43
    },
    {
      "content": "也可以想象让不同模型互相 critique",
      "from": 130.43,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 43,
      "to": 134.76
    },
    {
      "content": "可以设想使用专门的批评代理",
      "from": 134.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 44,
      "to": 136.88
    },
    {
      "content": "它只是被提示指令的组件",
      "from": 136.88,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 45,
      "to": 140.69
    },
    {
      "content": "例如你的角色是代码审查",
      "from": 140.69,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 46,
      "to": 142.65
    },
    {
      "content": "这里提供任务目标代码",
      "from": 142.65,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 47,
      "to": 144.27
    },
    {
      "content": "仔细检查代码并如此类推",
      "from": 144.27,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 48,
      "to": 145.72
    },
    {
      "content": "第二个批评代理可能指出错误或运行单元测试",
      "from": 145.72,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 49,
      "to": 149.84
    },
    {
      "content": "通过让两个模拟代理协作",
      "from": 149.84,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 50,
      "to": 153.16
    },
    {
      "content": "每个代理只是一个被提示扮演特定角色的语言模型",
      "from": 153.16,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 51,
      "to": 156.86
    },
    {
      "content": "你需要让他们来回迭代以获得更好的输出",
      "from": 156.86,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 52,
      "to": 161.21
    },
    {
      "content": "除了反思模式之外",
      "from": 161.21,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 53,
      "to": 163.17
    },
    {
      "content": "第二个重要的设计模式是使用",
      "from": 163.17,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 54,
      "to": 166.37
    },
    {
      "content": "今天可以赋予它们可以调用的功能来完成任务",
      "from": 166.37,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 55,
      "to": 172.67
    },
    {
      "content": "例如",
      "from": 172.67,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 56,
      "to": 173.41
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你询问",
      "from": 173.41,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 57,
      "to": 174.05
    },
    {
      "content": "你知道的",
      "from": 174.05,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 58,
      "to": 174.43
    },
    {
      "content": "什么是最好的咖啡机",
      "from": 174.43,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 59,
      "to": 175.77
    },
    {
      "content": "根据评测者",
      "from": 175.77,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 60,
      "to": 176.73
    },
    {
      "content": "并提供网络搜索功能",
      "from": 176.73,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 61,
      "to": 178.29
    },
    {
      "content": "然后它可以真正搜索互联网找到更优答案",
      "from": 178.29,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 62,
      "to": 182.26
    },
    {
      "content": "或者代码执行工具",
      "from": 182.26,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 63,
      "to": 183.9
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你问一个数学问题",
      "from": 183.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 64,
      "to": 185.24
    },
    {
      "content": "比如我投资一百美元",
      "from": 185.24,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 65,
      "to": 186.86
    },
    {
      "content": "复利计算",
      "from": 186.86,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 66,
      "to": 187.88
    },
    {
      "content": "无论你结束",
      "from": 187.88,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 67,
      "to": 188.68
    },
    {
      "content": "然后它可以编写并执行代码计算答案",
      "from": 188.68,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 68,
      "to": 192.38
    },
    {
      "content": "今天",
      "from": 192.38,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 69,
      "to": 192.9
    },
    {
      "content": "不同开发者为数学或数据分析提供了多种工具",
      "from": 192.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 70,
      "to": 198.56
    },
    {
      "content": "收集信息",
      "from": 198.56,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 71,
      "to": 199.7
    },
    {
      "content": "通过从网页获取内容",
      "from": 199.7,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 72,
      "to": 201.1
    },
    {
      "content": "或各种数据库",
      "from": 201.1,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 73,
      "to": 202.42
    },
    {
      "content": "与邮件等生产力应用交互",
      "from": 202.42,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 74,
      "to": 204.88
    },
    {
      "content": "日历等等",
      "from": 204.88,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 75,
      "to": 206.06
    },
    {
      "content": "以及处理图像",
      "from": 206.06,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 76,
      "to": 208.4
    },
    {
      "content": "等等更多",
      "from": 208.4,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 77,
      "to": 209.34
    },
    {
      "content": "语言模型决定使用哪些工具的能力",
      "from": 209.34,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 78,
      "to": 213.4
    },
    {
      "content": "即",
      "from": 213.4,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 79,
      "to": 213.74
    },
    {
      "content": "调用哪些函数让模型能完成更多任务",
      "from": 213.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 80,
      "to": 217.8
    },
    {
      "content": "第四种设计模式是规划",
      "from": 217.8,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 81,
      "to": 221.28
    },
    {
      "content": "这是来自《Hugging GPT》论文的例子",
      "from": 221.28,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 82,
      "to": 225.32
    },
    {
      "content": "当要求系统",
      "from": 225.32,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 83,
      "to": 229.22
    },
    {
      "content": "请生成一张女孩读书的图像",
      "from": 229.22,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 84,
      "to": 231.42
    },
    {
      "content": "图像中的男孩姿势相似",
      "from": 231.42,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 85,
      "to": 233.24
    },
    {
      "content": "然后请用你的声音描述新图像",
      "from": 233.24,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 86,
      "to": 235.32
    },
    {
      "content": "模型可以自动决定执行此任务",
      "from": 235.32,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 87,
      "to": 239.37
    },
    {
      "content": "首先需要找到姿势检测模型确定男孩姿势",
      "from": 239.37,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 88,
      "to": 244.5
    },
    {
      "content": "然后调整图像生成女孩画面",
      "from": 244.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 89,
      "to": 247.04
    },
    {
      "content": "并生成图像",
      "from": 247.04,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 90,
      "to": 247.68
    },
    {
      "content": "文本描述",
      "from": 247.68,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 91,
      "to": 248.12
    },
    {
      "content": "最后文本转语音",
      "from": 248.12,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 92,
      "to": 249.89
    },
    {
      "content": "因此在规划中，语言模型决定所需行动序列",
      "from": 249.89,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 93,
      "to": 255.91
    },
    {
      "content": "在此为API调用序列",
      "from": 255.91,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 94,
      "to": 259.64
    },
    {
      "content": "从而按正确顺序执行步骤",
      "from": 259.64,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 95,
      "to": 263.84
    },
    {
      "content": "完成任务",
      "from": 263.84,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 96,
      "to": 266.15
    },
    {
      "content": "而非开发者预先硬编码步骤",
      "from": 266.15,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 97,
      "to": 270.19
    },
    {
      "content": "这允许模型决定代理规划的步骤",
      "from": 270.19,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 98,
      "to": 275.66
    },
    {
      "content": "虽然更难控制且更具实验性",
      "from": 275.66,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 99,
      "to": 278.62
    },
    {
      "content": "但有时能产生惊艳结果",
      "from": 278.62,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 100,
      "to": 281.38
    },
    {
      "content": "然后最后是多智能体工作流",
      "from": 281.38,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 101,
      "to": 284.28
    },
    {
      "content": "就像人类经理可能会雇佣多人协作完成复杂项目",
      "from": 284.28,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 102,
      "to": 289.92
    },
    {
      "content": "在某些情况下，雇佣多个智能体可能更合理",
      "from": 289.92,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 103,
      "to": 294.42
    },
    {
      "content": "每个可能专注于不同领域",
      "from": 294.42,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 104,
      "to": 297.3
    },
    {
      "content": "并共同完成复杂任务",
      "from": 297.3,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 105,
      "to": 300.94
    },
    {
      "content": "你看到的这张图来自名为Chat Dev的项目",
      "from": 300.94,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 106,
      "to": 305.22
    },
    {
      "content": "这是陈倩及其合作者开发的软件框架Chat Dev",
      "from": 305.22,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 107,
      "to": 310.64
    },
    {
